	<div class="ab">
		<p class="ab2">Traditional methods of managing attendance, such as paper registers or spreadsheets, 
		are prone to errors, time-consuming, and lack automation. There is a need for a more efficient, 
		automated solution that ensures accurate tracking, easy accessibility, and reduces the administrative 
		burden on educational institutions.</p><br>
	
		<h2 class="ab1">Objectives & Goals</h2>
		<p class="ab2"><strong style="text-decoration:underline;">Real-Time Access:</strong> Ensure real-time 
		access to attendance data for students, teachers, and 
		administrators.<br>
		<strong style="text-decoration:underline;">Data Security:</strong> Secure and accurate storage of attendance 
		records in a MySQL database.<br>
		<strong style="text-decoration:underline;">User-Friendly Interface:</strong> A simple, intuitive interface built 
		with HTML and CSS, along with MYSQL DB making it easy for all 
		users to interact with the system.<br>
		<strong style="text-decoration:underline;">Custom Reports:</strong> Generate detailed reports based on attendance 
		data, enabling teachers and administrators 
		to identify trends and take necessary actions.<br>
		<strong style="text-decoration:underline;">Student Profile Management:</strong> Each students attendance record 
		is maintained, including the number of classes attended, missed, and overall attendance percentage.<br>
		
		<h2 class="ab1">Benefits</h2>
		<ul class="ul1"><li><strong>Schools and Colleges:</strong> Manage attendance efficiently for large numbers of students.</li>
		<li>Teachers: Save time and reduce paperwork.</li>
		<li>Students and Parents: Stay informed about attendance records and academic progress.</li></ul>>
